import React from 'react'
import { DetailContainer, DetailPart, HeaderContainer, ImgContainer, IngContainer, OtherPart } from './style'
import dI from '../../assets/default-image.jpg'

function Details() {
    return (
        <DetailContainer>
            <HeaderContainer>
                Header Container
                <ImgContainer>{dI}</ImgContainer>

            <DetailPart>
                <IngContainer>{dI}</IngContainer>
                <OtherPart>other</OtherPart>
            </DetailPart>
        </DetailContainer>
    )
}

export default Details
